      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Visa applicants across <a href="/locations/dubai/">Dubai</a>, <a href="/locations/abu-dhabi/">Abu Dhabi</a>, and <a href="/locations/sharjah/">Sharjah</a> need PCC translation for employment and <a href="/services/golden-visa-translation/">Golden Visa</a> applications. <a href="/industries/healthcare/">Healthcare professionals</a> require PCC translation for DHA and DOH licensing.</p>

